caller_intent: The caller is seeking assistance with a refund for an auto insurance policy they canceled approximately 2-3 months ago, which they believe they should have received but have not yet received.
resolution_steps: Agent asked clarifying questions about the policy cancellation (specifically whether the caller removed a vehicle or canceled a policy).
Agent requested the caller provide details about the vehicle (1995 Ranger) and the timeline of the cancellation.
Agent informed the caller they would transfer the call to another agent to assist further.
knowledge_required: Refund timelines and procedures for canceled policies
Internal systems to check refund status
summary: A caller contacted Alliance Insurance to inquire about a refund for an auto insurance policy canceled 2-3 months prior. The agent gathered details about the policy and vehicle involved, then offered to transfer the call to a specialist for further assistance. The outcome is pending as the call was not fully resolved.
